From 62148b4709a6e1a38c78355bc11c65b03e08a2bd Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sun, 13 Jul 2025 18:07:11 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: Add support for ring usage stats

Add new debugfs entry to display all ring stats includes
SW and HW head and tail pointers along with ring usage
which is measured in percentage of not used ring entries
with total number of ring entries.

cat /sys/kernel/debug/ath12k/pci-0002:01:00.0/dump_srng_stats
Last interrupt received for each CE:
CE_id 0 pipe_num 0 8749720ms before ce_manual_poll_count 0 ce_last_manual_tasklet_schedule_ts 8493860ms before
CE_id 1 pipe_num 1 270ms before ce_manual_poll_count 0 ce_last_manual_tasklet_schedule_ts 8493860ms before
CE_id 2 pipe_num 2 90ms before ce_manual_poll_count 0 ce_last_manual_tasklet_schedule_ts 8493860ms before
.
.
Last interrupt received for each group:
group_id         delay in ms
0           8493860ms
1           8493860ms
2           8493860ms
.
.
napi processed before 8754810ms
WBM_hw_idle_link:SW Head: 65534 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 0
WBM_hw_idle_link:HW Head: 65534 Tail: 720 Ring Usage 1
napi processed before 8751690ms
Reo_exception:SW Head: 0 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 0
Reo_exception:HW Head: 0 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 0
napi processed before 8493860ms
Reo_reinject:SW Head: 0 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 0
Reo_reinject:HW Head: 0 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 0
.
.
napi processed before 8751690ms
Rxdma_buf:SW Head: 16382 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 99
Rxdma_buf:HW Head: -1 Tail: -1 Ring Usage 0
napi processed before 8493860ms
Rxdma_monitor_dst:SW Head: 0 Tail: 0 Ring Usage 0
Rxdma_monitor_dst:HW Head: -1 Tail: -1 Ring Usage 0

Patch Dependency: 0204-a-ath12k-Add-fw-recovery-support.patch

Signed-off-by: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
